---
// 3-step code walkthrough. Braces in Go snippets are HTML-escaped so Astro
// doesn't parse them as template expressions.
---

<section class="stream">
  <div class="atlas-inner">
    <header class="head">
      <p class="eyebrow">STREAM WITH TOOLS</p>
      <h2>Chunks arrive as they're produced.</h2>
      <p class="intro">
        Open a streaming conversation, register an MCP tool, and let the model call it
        mid-stream. You'll see chunks arrive as they're produced, with the runtime
        handling the tool round-trip.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="steps">
      <article class="step">
        <div class="s-head">
          <div class="s-num">1 · Open a streaming conversation</div>
          <p class="s-desc">
            Same pack, same API — <code>Stream</code> returns a channel of chunks you range over.
          </p>
        </div>
        <pre class="s-code"><code>conv, _ := sdk.<span class="fn">Open</span>(<span class="s">"./app.pack.json"</span>, <span class="s">"chat"</span>)
<span class="k">defer</span> conv.<span class="fn">Close</span>()

<span class="k">for</span> chunk := <span class="k">range</span> conv.<span class="fn">Stream</span>(ctx, msg) &#123;
  <span class="k">if</span> chunk.Type == sdk.ChunkDone &#123;
    <span class="k">break</span>
  &#125;
  fmt.<span class="fn">Print</span>(chunk.Text)
&#125;</code></pre>
      </article>

      <article class="step">
        <div class="s-head">
          <div class="s-num">2 · Register an MCP tool</div>
          <p class="s-desc">
            Point the runtime at a live MCP server. Tools are discovered and callable the
            moment the conversation opens.
          </p>
        </div>
        <pre class="s-code"><code>conv, _ := sdk.<span class="fn">Open</span>(<span class="s">"./app.pack.json"</span>, <span class="s">"chat"</span>,
  sdk.<span class="fn">WithMCP</span>(<span class="s">"filesystem"</span>,
    <span class="s">"npx"</span>,
    <span class="s">"@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem"</span>,
    <span class="s">"./data"</span>,
  ),
)</code></pre>
      </article>

      <article class="step">
        <div class="s-head">
          <div class="s-num">3 · Watch the metrics</div>
          <p class="s-desc">
            Every stage emits Prometheus metrics. Scrape them and gate on them.
          </p>
        </div>
        <pre class="s-code"><code><span class="prompt">$</span> curl -s :9090/metrics \
  | grep promptkit_

<span class="cmt"># in-flight gauge, retry budget,</span>
<span class="cmt"># first-chunk latency histogram</span>
promptkit_inflight_streams 1000
promptkit_first_chunk_ms_p50 41</code></pre>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stream {
    padding: 76px 30px 84px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    background: var(--surface-1);
  }
  .head {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 44px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--nebula-violet);
  }
  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 1.12;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--star-100);
  }
  .intro {
    margin: 16px auto 0;
    max-width: 620px;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--star-600);
  }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    background: var(--surface-card);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .s-head {
    padding: 18px 20px 14px;
  }
  .s-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--nebula-violet);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .s-desc {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--star-600);
  }
  .s-desc code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.88em;
    color: var(--nebula-violet);
  }
  .s-code {
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    background: var(--surface-code);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--star-400);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .s-code .k {
    color: var(--nebula-violet);
  }
  .s-code .fn {
    color: var(--starlight-200);
  }
  .s-code .s {
    color: var(--pulsar-300);
  }
  .s-code .prompt {
    color: var(--star-700);
  }
  .s-code .cmt {
    color: var(--star-800);
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
